article.description: — Hakim Byrd had 20 points as Marist romped past Manhattan 61-39 on Saturday.
article.headline: Byrd scores 20 to lift Marist over Manhattan 61-39
article.linkText: Byrd scores 20 to lift Marist over Manhattan 61-39
article.story: RIVERDALE, N.Y. -- — Hakim Byrd had 20 points as Marist romped past Manhattan 61-39 on Saturday. Ricardo Wright had 12 points for Marist (4-1, 2-1 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Braden Bell added 12 points and Raheim Sullivan had 10 points. Byrd shot 4 for 6 from deep. Anthony Nelson had 11 points for the Jaspers (1-2, 1-2). Samba Diallo added seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
